comments: Brogdon (IND) goes to, not through, White's (SAS) space along the sideline.
White (SAS) briefly has his arms around Sabonis' (IND) upper half before correcting.
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in White's (SAS) path and does not deliver the contact. Sabonis and White briefly engage and disengage with one another thereafter.
Gay (SAS) makes marginal contact with Brogdon's (IND) side during his driving shot attempt.
Gay (SAS) brushes the netting while defending the baseline drive and shot attempt.
White (SAS) makes marginal contact with Sabonis' (IND) right side during rebounding.
Gay (SAS) and Sabonis (IND) make incidental arm contact with one another during rebounding.
Mills (SAS) beats Brogdon (IND) to the spot and establishes legal guarding position prior to Brogdon driving through him after the pass is made.
Sabonis (IND) and Gay (SAS) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.
Sabonis (IND) hedges the pick and delivers contact to White's (SAS) side that affects his SQBR.
Gay (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position and slightly extends his lower half into Brogdon's (IND) path prior to contact being made.
Mills (SAS) extends his leg as part of his natural shooting motion; any contact from Turner (IND) is deemed incidental.
White (SAS) briefly has his arms around Sabonis' (IND) upper half before correcting.
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in White's (SAS) path and does not deliver the contact.
White (SAS) cleanly dislodges the ball during Sabonis' (IND) shot attempt.
Turner (IND) makes slight contact with Mills' (SAS) right arm as he drives along the baseline.
Available angles show, Mills' (SAS) heel remains raised above the sideline at the start of his dribble.
White (SAS) establishes his right foot as his pivot after picking up his dribble and maintains it as he passes the ball.
Sabonis (IND) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Brogdon (IND) briefly has his arms around DeRozan's (SAS) upper half before correcting.
Holiday (IND) makes marginal contact with Lyles' (SAS) left side as he receives the pass.
Turner (IND) jumps vertically and absorbs the body contact made with Lyles (SAS) before cleanly blocking Lyles' shot attempt thereafter.
Turner (IND) brushes Gay's (SAS) off-arm during his shot attempt.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
White (SAS) commits the take foul on Brogdon (IND).
White (SAS) commits a take foul on Turner (IND).
